    <item>
      <title>由于价格剧烈波动控制市场，可可下跌 17%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/cocoa-slumps-on-better-mid-crop-outlook-and-lower-bullish-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约可可期货价格暴跌近 17%，伦敦可可期货价格也大幅下跌，由于越来越少的公司能够承受交易成本的上升，导致市场价格容易出现大幅波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/cocoa-slumps-on-better-mid-crop-outlook-and-lower-bullish-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 10:10:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
